Khufu ship.0076	Remains of Old Kingdom boats were found at Tarkhan -LRB- at least one boat -RRB- A ` model estate ' and funerary boat was found at Saqqara by W. Emery -LRB- in 1957-8 ; tomb S 3357 -RRB- .
