Lebor GabÃ¡la Ãrenn.0093	Tuatha DÃ© Danann The Tuatha DÃ© Danann are descendants of another group of the scattered seed of Nemed .
Lebor GabÃ¡la Ãrenn.0094	They return to Ireland from the far north , where they have learned the arts of pagan magic and druidry , on or about May 1 .
